=Description=

This Hangout app will enable you to share and watch your public photos together with the other participants.

You can test the app by starting a hangout from here: http://www.allmyplus.com/hangout-photo-share/


=Installation=

  * Edit photos.xml and photos.js and change <YOUR PATH> to where you plan to upload the files.

  * Upload all the files to <YOUR PATH>

  * Please note that the files need to be publicly accessible.

  * Go to https://code.google.com/apis/console/ and create a new project.

  * Activate the "Google+ Hangouts API" in Services.

  * Go to "Hangouts" and put the full URL to <YOUR PATH>comments.xml in "Gadget URL"

  * Save and you are ready to "Enter a hangout!" :)


